<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="container mt-4 mb-5">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Terms & Conditions</h1>

    <h4>1. Eligibility</h4>
    <p>
        Users must be at least 21 years old and possess a valid driving license.
        Only registered drivers are allowed to operate the rented vehicle.
    </p>

    <h4>2. Booking & Payment</h4>
    <p>
        Booking can be made online, but payment must be completed offline at the time of vehicle pickup.
        A refundable security deposit may be required. Rental prices do not include fuel, fines, or penalties.
    </p>

    <h4>3. Vehicle Usage</h4>
    <p>
        Vehicles must be used responsibly and only for legal purposes.
        Misuse such as racing, illegal activities, or driving under the influence is strictly prohibited.
    </p>

    <h4>4. Return Policy</h4>
    <p>
        Vehicles must be returned on time and in the same condition.
        Late returns or unclean vehicles may result in additional charges.
    </p>

    <h4>5. Damage & Liability</h4>
    <p>
        The renter is responsible for any damage, theft, or loss during the rental period.
        In case of an accident, authorities and the company must be informed immediately.
    </p>

    <h4>6. Cancellation Policy</h4>
    <p>
        Free cancellation is allowed up to 72 hours before booking.
        Late cancellations may incur charges.
    </p>

    <hr class="my-5">

    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <h4>1. Information We Collect</h4>
    <p>
        We collect personal details such as name, contact information, ID proof,
        and driving license for verification purposes.
    </p>

    <h4>2. Use of Information</h4>
    <p>
        Your data is used to manage bookings, verify identity, and improve our services.
    </p>

    <h4>3. Data Protection</h4>
    <p>
        We ensure your data is stored securely and not shared unnecessarily.
    </p>

    <h4>4. Data Sharing</h4>
    <p>
        Data may be shared with legal authorities if required by law.
    </p>

    <h4>5. Consent</h4>
    <p>
        By using our platform, you agree to our Terms & Privacy Policy.
    </p>
</div>